I want to say a big thank you for coming today.

7
00:00:19,931 --> 00:00:22,253
So we're going to be together for about one hour.

8
00:00:22,353 --> 00:00:24,154
And I hope it will be both informative

9
00:00:24,194 --> 00:00:25,555
and that we can have fun together as well.

