and we stuck with DualShock 4 because it is perfect for us.

492
00:23:10,067 --> 00:23:12,248
It's trackable, but also it has an analog stick.

493
00:23:12,548 --> 00:23:14,509
And the button alignment was perfect for jumping

494
00:23:14,549 --> 00:23:16,169
and punching for these kind of platform games.

495
00:23:16,889 --> 00:23:18,610
And the controls are super simple on purpose.

496
00:23:19,210 --> 00:23:23,691
We thought that the VR would be what would add richness.

497
00:23:24,332 --> 00:23:26,032
So the control scheme could be very, very simple.

498
00:23:26,412 --> 00:23:29,033
The richness of the game should come from everything

