00:23:43,665 --> 00:23:46,347
It felt nice and chunky in your hands,

506
00:23:46,427 --> 00:23:47,667
and that's what we did.

507
00:23:49,508 --> 00:23:52,270
Also, the guns are, the gadgets are effectively guns.

