00:25:45,593 --> 00:25:47,135
For example, the water gadget had something

546
00:25:47,155 --> 00:25:49,717
like 10 use cases, ranging from making platforms,

547
00:25:50,157 --> 00:25:51,899
defeating enemies, but also having this kind

