00:25:55,423 --> 00:25:58,346
So the gadget section, they're generally scripted inside the level.

550
00:25:58,386 --> 00:25:59,506
It's quite a specific location.

551
00:25:59,566 --> 00:26:01,788
However, within those predefined sections,

552
00:26:01,848 --> 00:26:03,149
there is room for self-expression.

553
00:26:03,189 --> 00:26:05,110
So example here, the player is playing it safe.

554
00:26:05,711 --> 00:26:08,092
You can pull all the platforms one by one.

555
00:26:08,973 --> 00:26:10,434
But we made sure there was also some ways

556
00:26:10,474 --> 00:26:12,696
to kind of use the gadget in a skillful way.

557
00:26:12,716 --> 00:26:15,458
So here you can tug on a rope to send asteroid.

558
00:26:17,839 --> 00:26:20,481
And equally, this is a shuriken, so you can play really safe.

559
00:26:20,501 --> 00:26:24,323
You can make like a very, very, you know, safe path with small germs.

560
00:26:25,644 --> 00:26:27,765
Or you can go for a kind of more risky approach.

561
00:26:27,785 --> 00:26:32,868
So, we also made sure that the gadgets kind of have this kind of dual, dual, you know,

562
00:26:32,948 --> 00:26:36,070
couple levels of, of, of skill, really.

563
00:26:38,475 --> 00:26:42,516
Right, earlier I mentioned the gadgets were all like, you know, remote guns but I've allied

564
00:26:42,596 --> 00:26:46,877
because one of them is actually based on 3D position and that's the way where you plug

