00:28:13,634 --> 00:28:16,114
so that in the game you're using square and cross,

591
00:28:16,294 --> 00:28:19,115
which are your punch and jump buttons.

592
00:28:19,655 --> 00:28:20,555
And that's really nice actually,

593
00:28:20,595 --> 00:28:22,375
because it means that you can actually make do with,

594
00:28:22,475 --> 00:28:24,336
you know, you can get rid of tutorials in a way,

595
00:28:24,376 --> 00:28:26,056
because you don't have to remind the player

596
00:28:26,076 --> 00:28:27,096
which buttons to use,

597
00:28:27,396 --> 00:28:29,497
they're just the ones that he can see on the controller.

