00:29:05,939 --> 00:29:08,540
But we changed the colors, the lighting, the vegetation,

614
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:10,220
so it never felt like the same location twice.

615
00:29:11,332 --> 00:29:13,632
And well, there is an expense to that, of course,

616
00:29:13,932 --> 00:29:15,133
making everything a little bit unique.

